Label: 3d seismics
Description: Geophysical measurement used to record acoustic response of seismic sources over an area in order to define 3D seismic property distribution in a volume of the earth.

Label: radar interferometry
Description: Radar mapping technique used to detect centimeter-sized changes in the Earth's crust due to natural phenomena.

Label: sonar
Description: Sound Navigation And Ranging system used for underwater mapping
